{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"1e6d462fba","title":"刘少奇对北京师大一附中工作组的指示","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"e4e4af475f","index":0,"year":1966,"month":6,"day":21,"articleId":"1e6d462fba"}],"tags":[{"id":"2d13338754","name":"指示","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"3aaab89c2a","name":"刘少奇","type":"人物"},{"id":"70f02a0dc7","name":"资产阶级反动路线","type":"主题"},{"id":"c20d333791","name":"关键人物文稿","type":"文稿大类"},{"id":"ed8d454915","name":"刘少奇","type":"主题"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"wenku","name":"中国文化大革命文库(第一版)","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"db","author":"宋永毅","files":""}],"authors":[{"id":"9986567b57","name":"刘少奇"}]},"publication_details":{"wenku":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"dfeb9ee4fb","type":"title","text":"刘少奇对北京师大一附中工作组的指示","index":0,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"1e6d462fba"},{"id":"140c6b089f","type":"paragraph","text":"一、写大字报的人，就是打着红旗反红旗。但不要对他们说。写大字报的非常可疑，是不是黑帮分子不肯定。","index":1,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"1e6d462fba"},{"id":"2d0df2e9f9","type":"paragraph","text":"二、辩论一下就不要辩论，还要团结嘛。只要大多数赞成就可以了。让他们保留意见。可以再看嘛。","index":2,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"1e6d462fba"},{"id":"c6a35465bd","type":"paragraph","text":"三、教师，不要说人家是假检讨。还是需要假检讨，也证实一些问题，但要说是不够的。投机也不怕，投你们机也投的革命的机。人家投到你那里，为什么不要人家。但要警惕，不能篡夺领导岗位。","index":3,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"1e6d462fba"},{"id":"3567df6896","type":"paragraph","text":"尽量争取老师。","index":4,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"1e6d462fba"},{"id":"7e6e23e0ec","type":"paragraph","text":"同学们不信任老师，这就是群众初步发动起来的表现。","index":5,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"1e6d462fba"}],"page":{"id":"3da5118a3f","publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"1e6d462fba","start":0,"end":0}}}},"__N_SSG":true}